(8, 1, '2019-07-06 18:32:09', '2019-07-06 18:32:09', '<p>                                our services</p>		\n			<h2>HeadShots Photography provides  photography services for executives, corporations, and professional businesses. We also offer acting and modeling head shots as part of our studio services. We offer same day service on most projects and 24 hours on all projects.</h2>		\n				<a href=\"#\">\n				</a>\n				<h3>\n					<a href=\"#\">PHOTOGRAPHY</a>\n				</h3>\n				<p>Our photography is used for company websites, LinkedIn, Facebook,  marketing print material,  audition photos for actors, model portfolios, and individual creative portraits.\n</p>\n				<figure><img src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/shutterstock_237625108.jpg\" alt=\"shutterstock_237625108\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/photo_2019-07-06_18-52-37.jpg\" alt=\"photo_2019-07-06_18-52-37\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/eth-ham-el-05_screen-1.jpg\" alt=\"Hamer-Children\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/aesp.biz-afr.jpg\" alt=\"hHamer\" /></figure>			\n			<a href=\"#Photography\" role=\"button\">\n						More Information\n					</a>\n				<a href=\"#\">\n				</a>\n				<h3>\n					<a href=\"#\">VIDEOGRAPHY</a>\n				</h3>\n				<p>The Passion of the Christ is a 2004 American biblical drama film directed by Mel Gibson, written ... He attempts to have Jesus freed by the peoples\' choice between Jesus and violent criminal Barabbas. </p>\n		https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3Ob9dOYkLjA?v=XHOmBV4js_E		\n			<a href=\"#Photography\" role=\"button\">\n						More Information\n					</a>\n				<a href=\"#\">\n				</a>\n				<h3>\n					<a href=\"#\">DESGING</a>\n				</h3>\n				<p>Basically I have fall in love with photography and videography since 2012. I’ve touched my professional camera nine to-five. I’ve captured everything, learned it anyway. Until now. </p>\n				<figure><img src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/shutterstock_237625108.jpg\" alt=\"shutterstock_237625108\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/photo_2019-07-06_18-52-37.jpg\" alt=\"photo_2019-07-06_18-52-37\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/eth-ham-el-05_screen-1.jpg\" alt=\"Hamer-Children\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/aesp.biz-afr.jpg\" alt=\"hHamer\" /></figure>			\n			<a href=\"#Photography\" role=\"button\">\n						More Information\n					</a>\n		<h2>PHOTOGRAPHY</h2><p>My life is surrounded by artist and creative workers. I learned everyday from tattoo artist, illustrator, graphic designer, and UI/UX designer.</p><p>My life is surrounded by artist and creative workers. I learned everyday from tattoo artist, illustrator, graphic designer, and UI/UX designer.</p><p>My life is surrounded by artist and creative workers. I learned everyday from tattoo artist, illustrator, graphic designer, and UI/UX designer</p>		\n			<a href=\"#http://localhost/aberaphotography/contact\" role=\"button\">\n						Get In Contact\n					</a>\n		https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SAngaG20INQ?v=XHOmBV4js_E		\n			<figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"6ff31827\" href=\'http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/shutterstock_237625108.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/shutterstock_237625108-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</figure><figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"6ff31827\" href=\'http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/hamrar.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\