thiopia-8-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</figure><figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"6ff31827\" href=\'http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/sunsetcaravan.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/sunsetcaravan-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</figure><figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"6ff31827\" href=\'http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Africa-Photography-National-Geographic-Omo-Valley-Africa-.jpg\'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Africa-Photography-National-Geographic-Omo-Valley-Africa--150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n			</figure>\n		<h2>VIDEOGRAPHY</h2>\n<p>My life is surrounded by artist and creative workers. I learned everyday from tattoo artist, illustrator, graphic designer, and UI/UX designer.My life is surrounded by artist and creative workers. I learned everyday from tattoo artist, illustrator, graphic designer, and UI/UX designer.My life is surrounded by artist and creative workers. I learned everyday from tattoo artist, illustrator, graphic designer, and UI/UX designer</p>		\n			<a href=\"#http://localhost/aberaphotography/contact\" role=\"button\">\n						Get In Contact\n					</a>\n		<p>                                        <a href=\"#portfolio\">portifolio</a></p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DicOQJE3d8U?v=XHOmBV4js_E		\n			<h2>samrawit and Teddy<br>weeding</h2>		\n		<p><b>Ethiopia</b> is the <b>26th</b>-largest country in the world by area (1,104,300 total sq. km). The top 10 countries and dependencies by area are: World, Russia, Antarctica, Canada, China, United States, Brazil, Australia, India, Argentina, Kazakhstan, Algeria.</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n					<a href=\"https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/#inbox\">						\n										email me\n											</a>\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width=\"1000\" height=\"750\" src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Hamer-Tribe-Ethiopia-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Hamer-Tribe-Ethiopia-8.jpg 1000w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Hamer-Tribe-Ethiopia-8-300x225.jpg 300w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Hamer-Tribe-Ethiopia-8-768x576.jpg 768w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Hamer-Tribe-Ethiopia-8-830x623.jpg 830w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Hamer-Tribe-Ethiopia-8-230x173.jpg 230w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Hamer-Tribe-Ethiopia-8-350x263.jpg 350w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Hamer-Tribe-Ethiopia-8-480x360.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" />											\n			<h2>Hammer Girl </h2>		\n		<p><b>Ethiopia</b>, <b>Hamer</b> Tribe. The <b>Hamer</b>, or Hamar, are an Omotic community inhabiting southwestern <b>Ethiopia</b>. They inhabit the territory east of the Omo River and have villages in Turmi and Dimeka. The 2007 national census reported 46,532 people in this ethnic group, of whom 957 were urban inhabitants.</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n					<a href=\"https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/#inbox\">						\n										email me\n											</a>\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n										<img width=\"2560\" height=\"1600\" src=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600.jpg 2560w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-300x188.jpg 300w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-768x480.jpg 768w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-1024x640.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-830x519.jpg 830w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-230x144.jpg 230w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-350x219.jpg 350w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-480x300.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />											\n			<h2>Landscape shoot</h2>		\n		<p>Gonder Landscape architecture is a profession which places high value on the regional context; so our curriculum needs to be tailored to address problem solving within the regional, environmental, social and economic realms,” said Joachim Dieter, Scientific Director of The Ethiopian Institute of Architecture, Building Construction and City Development (EiABC)</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n					<a href=\"https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/#inbox\">						\n										email me\n											</a>\n									</li>\n						</ul>', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2019-07-08 18:39:40', '2019-07-08 18:39:40', '', 0, 'http://localhost/aberaphotography/?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
