nds_2560x1600-768x480.jpg 768w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-1024x640.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-830x519.jpg 830w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-230x144.jpg 230w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-350x219.jpg 350w, http://localhost/aberaphotography/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/ws_Scotland_Highlands_2560x1600-480x300.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />											\n			<h2>Landscape shoot</h2>		\n		<p>Gonder Landscape architecture is a profession which places high value on the regional context; so our curriculum needs to be tailored to address problem solving within the regional, environmental, social and economic realms,” said Joachim Dieter, Scientific Director of The Ethiopian Institute of Architecture, Building Construction and City Development (EiABC)</p>		\n					<ul>\n							<li >\n					<a href=\"https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/#inbox\">						\n										email me\n											</a>\n									</li>\n						</ul>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-08 18:39:40', '2019-07-08 18:39:40', '', 8, 'http://localhost/aberaphotography/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
